 High-Frequency Trading (HFT) 
 
 HFT runs on Linux only.

 Production HFT = Linux
 Windows/macOS = no
 
 Linux knowledge is mandatory

----------------------------------
Must-learn
    Modern C++ (move, allocators, cache)
    Linux internals
    Networking (UDP/TCP, multicast)
    Lock-free programming
    CPU & memory optimization
    Order book design

Mini HFT-style projects
    Market data feed parser
    In-memory order book
    Event-driven trading simulator
    Latency benchmark tool

